           SHORT="Gnomeradio is a FM radio tuner for the GNOME"
cat << EOF
Gnomeradio is a FM radio tuner for the GNOME desktop
(version 1 and 2). It should work with every FM tuner card
that is supported by video4linux. Remote controls are
supported via (optional) lirc-support. Gnomeradio can
also record radio as a Wave, MP3 or Ogg files.
EOF
